==Transportation== The shrine can be reached by [[:en:Kamayama Station|Kamayama Station]] on the Wakayama Electric Railway [[:en:Kishigawa Line|Kishigawa Line]].<ref>{{cite news |title=人の手を借りる、たま駅長 貴志駅（和歌山県、和歌山電鉄貴志川線） |url=http://www.asahi.com/travel/hitoekigatari/TKY201102280171.html |access-date=15 May 2020 |agency=[[The Asahi Shimbun]] |date=1 March 2011 |language=ja}}</ref>
